      • ListConverter

        public ListConverter(Converter<I> itemConverter,
                     String delimiters)

        Creates a new list converter with the given converter for the items and the given delimiters for the items. Any character in delimiters is considered a delimiter when parsing the string. The first character will be used when items are joined in a textual representation.

        Parameters:
        itemConverter - the converter for the items
        delimiters - the delimiters
